OL,3,CHundreds face homelessness after flats
OL,4,Cdeclared unsafe
OL,6,FKnowsley Council - which does not own
OL,7,For manage them - says responsibility
OL,8,Fhas changed several times since 2017
OL,9,Fwith different management agents being
OL,10,Fappointed but only remaining involved
OL,11,Ffor short periods.
OL,13,FThe latest company to take on that
OL,14,Frole two years ago claimed it tried to
OL,15,Fmake improvements but inherited a
OL,16,Fdevelopment that had suffered from
OL,17,Fyears of neglect.
