OL,4,Cdeclared unsafe
OL,6,FNow MFRS says it is not safe for
OL,7,Fpeople to live there because
OL,8,F"essential repairs" have not been
OL,9,Fcarried out.
OL,11,FThey will have to move out as soon as
OL,12,Fa temporary safety measure is
OL,13,Fwithdrawn.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "We understand
OL,16,Fthat this is disruptive and unpleasant
OL,17,Ffor residents, however all other
OL,18,Foptions have been exhausted and the
OL,19,Fsafety of residents is of paramount
OL,20,Fimportance. "
