OL,4,Cdeclared unsafe
OL,6,FThe council is in the process of
OL,7,Fcontacting all residents to offer
OL,8,Fsupport, which could include emergency
OL,9,Fre-housing.
OL,11,FCllr Graham Morgan, leader of Knowsley
OL,12,FCouncil, said: "These residents have
OL,13,Fbeen let down and neglected for years
OL,14,Fby the various private sector
OL,15,Fcompanies involved in the ownership
OL,16,Fand management of these buildings.
OL,18,F"They have been allowed to deteriorate
OL,19,Finto a terrible condition, with false
OL,20,Fpromises made about repairs that have
OL,21,Fnever materialised."
